snippet.title: Togges - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a Trailer!

Togges is a Collect-A-Thon 3D Platformer about adorable little cubes in an adventure to dominate the universe and save the galaxy!

This trailer was part of the "Hubworld Direct" - A collective between indie developers creating amazing 3D Platformers:

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1550270/Togges

GOG.com: https://www.gog.com/en/game/togges

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

 Contact: contact@togges.com.br

Site - http://www.togges.com.br/

Twitter - https://twitter.com/ToggesGame 

Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/togges.game/ 

Channel Togges - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1XVnUucQXJ_QXpt99ikJ7w/featured

Video link - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I0Pw3UZRvKQ&ab_channel=Togges

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
